<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>GOSPEL ACCLAMATION (LENT - a)</B></FONT></H2>
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">According to the Liturgical year (A-B-C) and according to the week (from 1st to 5th))
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">we do the acclamation planned by the Lectionary with one of the following two melodies:</FONT>
<H3><PRE>
