</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   A           Bm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.   "I know my sheep and they follow me!"
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   A           Bm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.   "I know my sheep and they follow me!"
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       D                G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C+A.  Praise to you o Christ...



